---
title: Cherry Tomato & Portabello Mushroom Pizza with Caramelised Onion, Double Cheese & Rocket
description: Forget the excessively saucy, topping-heavy pizzas of your past; here’s a simple pizza that will impress the whole family’s eyes
(and tastebuds). Here, quality ingredients like meaty mushrooms, tinned cherry tomatoes and crumbly Greek-style cheese ensure each bite packs a punch of flavour for no ordinary weeknight dinner.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
